refsection.programlisting:

load(GROCERDIR+'/data/BusinessSurvey.dat');
y=explone(['pp','fp','gpp','gob','fob','in'])
r=fac_pca1(y,1:2,2,'no','stan')
// With French business survey variables, on standardized variables (option 'stan'),
// calculates the first 2 factors, stores all results for these 2 factors.
// The # of factors being imposed by the user, the Bai-Ng option is set to 'no'.
